{"/service/ndnp/txdn/batch_txdn_bravo_ver01/data/sn86090383/00175034717/1908052201/0138.xml":{"full_text":"pv\nsSlpspiP\nbusiness streets and the building ol\nthe State Railroad into this city prom\nise to increase the payiolls here and\nmake new business for the town It\nis believed the street paving will be\nunder way within the next few\nweeks and the money paid out here\nincident to this work is going to help\nyto make it the good old summer time\nin reality Once started this work\nwill employ a big force of wage cam\ners and the money will be paid out\nlocally for supplies The railroad\nproposition should be closed up and\nthis work started shortly and this wili\nhelp matters considerably In addi\ntion to this work the big storms have\nmade it necessary for the expenditure\nof vast sums here in the way of re\nbuilding and repairing The watei\ncompany alone will expend possibly\n15000 or 1G000 within the next twr\nmonths in wages to day laborers and\nthis money will find its way into local\nbusiness circles And the I G N\nrailroad is having to spend vast sums\nin rebuilding bridges and track in\nthis territory and much of this monej\nis being paid to local people Alto\ngether these things should make busi\nness good here this summer With\nthis additional amount of money com\ning in together with the returns from\nthe truck fields etc Palestine should\nbe a busy place for some time\nWe want information Is Col\nWynne still running for attorney gen\neral and if so where is he running\nat\nThe Elks Minstiel contributed to\nthe gayety of life and for every smile\nafforded we return a complement of\nthanks\nTo the whole people Boil the drink\ning water and bum the trash and\nhelp to prolong life and magnify the\nbeautiful\nTo the Texas press gang Mineral\nWells Is one of the best towns on\nearth in which to familiarize ones\nself with the water wagon Ride her\nThe newspaper men in session in\nMineral Wells should throw the har\npoon into those fellows who denied\nthem the right of contract Open the\nvitrol boys\nCongressman Lillejs light has gone\nout as a refonner Lilley should\nhave rehearsed his chirgcs and tried\nGBScheer\nExpert Piano\nTuner\nLeave orders with\nBarnes Music Co\nTHE PALESTINE DAILY HERALD\nentered In the Palestine Texas Postofflce as SecondClass Mall Matter\nPUBLISHED EVERY AFTERNOON SUNDAY EXCEPTED\nW M AND H V HAMILTON JR\nEditors and Proprietors\nTELEPHONE 4 44\nThe HamiltonBoys You Know\nSUBSCRIPTION 15 CENTS THE WEEK BY THE YEAR 600\nNOTICE TO THE PUBLIC\nAny erroneous reflection upon the character standing or reputation of\nany person firm or corporation which may appear in the columns of The\nHerald will be gladly corrected upon It being brought to the attention of\nthe publishers\nPALESTINE TEXAS MAY 22 1908\nMAY 22 IN HISTORY\n1GS8 Alexander Pope\nborn Died May\nEnglish poet\n30 1744\n1755 Tench Coxe the rather of the\ncotton industry in the United\nStates born in Philadelphia\nDied thereJuly 17 1S24\n1S02 Martha Washington wife of\nGeorge Washington died at ML\nVernon Born in New Kent\ncounty Virginia in 1732\n1813 Marshal Duroc one of Napo\nleons most celebrated officers\nKilled at Reichenbach\n1849 Maria Edgworth English novel\nist died\n1S57 Paul Morton former secretary\nof the navy of the United\nStates born\n18G7 Queen Victoria issued a procla\nmation for uniting the provinces\nof Canada Nova Scotia and\nNew Brunswick into one domin\nion\n1S98 Edward Bellamy author of\nLooking Backward died\nBorn March 2G 1S50\nBUSINESS IN SIGHT\nThe business outlook for Palestine\nat this time is good if once we can\nget things going Besides the regular\nchannels of business which we haye\na right to expect to continue as good\nas usual the paving of two additional\nthem out before Springing them\njumped before he looked\nHe\nIt is a matter of record that no\nbonds ever issued by Palestine have\never been allowed to mature but have\nalways been paid for in advance That\nrecord ought to help some\nSenator Piatt a gay old boy with\none foot in the grave refused point\nblank Ho put the other in a divorce\ncase especially in a case where if he\nwas married he did not know it\nCaptain Bill McDonald of Texas\nwho is in Washington has accepted\nan invitation to dine at the White\nHouse Big game yet unkilled will\nno doubt be the toast of the occasion\nThe Dallas Times KCrald says the\nMexicans down in the Rio Grande\ncountryare still voting for Senor Bil\nlie Bailey and there is no telling what\nhis majority will finally be down\nthere\nBill Bryan vs Bill Taft will be the\nnext important case to be tried by the\npeoples tribunal Taft comes under\nthe indictment of being too handsome\nfor a man and too fat for a woman\nwhile Bryan has two defeats to ex\nplain away\nFjfty cents a barrel is the quotation\non drinking water now Palestine\nHerald\nGee whiz and it araining Nacog\nloches Sentinel\nThat is the trouble It rained all of\nthe water out of our waterworks\nThese specialists often play havoc\nwith peoples calculations Mae Wood\nhad old Senator Piatt backed into the\ncorner over that marriage claim until\nan expert stationer came along and\ntestified that the certificate showing\nthe marriage was not printed until a\nyear after the alleged date of the\nmarriage And then it was to jail for\nMae Isnt it shocking\nThe Herald has received a card\nfrom George Mendell for years staff\ncorrespondent of the Houston Chron\nicle at Austin announcing that he has\nabandoned the newspaper field and\nesumed the practice of law As the\nDallas Times Herald remarks how\nlie mighty has fallen Mendell is a\ngraduate of the law department of the\nState University\nThe 1 G N has been running\nspecial onion trains out of Texas for\nseveral weelts and now the fruit and\nmelon trains are to get busy Thus\nTexas adds to the joy of living at so\nmuch a car load and cheap at that\nHundreds of additional cars could\nfind ready markets among the hungry\npeople of less favored sections Poor\nold world outside of Texas\nNotable Track and Field Events\nSpecial to the Herald\nKansas City Mo May 22 Never\nbefore in the history of the Missouri\nValley Conference has there been\nsuch a wealth of runners leapers and\nweight hurlers of high grade as are\nerfteied for the annual meet that is\nto he held tomorrow at Elm Ridge\nPark The state universities as well\nas the smaller colleges of Missouri\nand Kansas will send their best men\nand additional Interest will be given\nby the participation for the first time\nof representatives from Ames Drake\nand the University of Nebraska\nSchool Social Life\nSpecial to the Herald\nBoston Mass May 22 Tho school\nin its social aspects was the chief\ntopic of consideration at the annual\nmeeting of the New England Assocla\nHon of School Superintendents held\ntoday at the Boston Latin School\nProf Henry Suzzallo of the teachers\ncollege or Columbia University Geo\nE Johnson of Pittsburg and Dr Al\nbert E Winshlp of Boston were the\nprincipal speakers\nThe Olympla Opera Company\nManager Swift of the Temple Opera\nHouse announces thathe has secured\nthe Olympla Opera company for Ills\nhouse for the entire week of June fif\nteenth This company Is well known\nhere and will prove a gobd drawing\ncard\nGet tho Habit Cook With Gas\nSycamore street says\nconstant soreness across my back\nand when stooping or exerting myself\nthe pain became very sharp If I took\ncold it always settled In my kidneys\ncausing extra pain and annoyance I\ntried different remedies but nona\nbrought permanent results pr I would\nnot have gone to the Bra j n Drug\nCo s store for Doans KUTfiey Pills\nIn a very short time the remedy\ndrove the pain away OtherLmembeis\nof the family have used DoansKld\nney Pills receiving the greajtest bene\nfit Doans Kidney Pills inj my case\nacted as represented andi heartily\nrecommend them at evern opportu\nnity as the best remedy I ever used\nFor sale by all dealers Price 50\ncents FosterMilburn Co Buffalo\nNew York sole agents for the United\nStates\nRemember the name Downs and\ntake no other\nCORRECT DRESS\nStarts with the proper Corset Model\nTo have the correct model you must\nfind the merchant that carries an as\nsortment for every figure and a fit\nter who can give you just what you\nneed The Model has all these and\nalso a private parlor built especially\nfor this department\nHAPPY WOMEN\nPlenty of Them In Palestine and\nGood Reason For It\nWouldnt any woman be happy\nAfter years of backache suffering\nDays of misery nights of unrest\nThe distress of urinary troubles\nShe finds relief and cure\nNo reason why any Palestine read\ner\nShould suffer in the face of\ndence like this\nMrs M C Hillyer formerly resid\ning in Palestine Texas at 405 North\nV\nevi\nThere was a\nGat tho Habit Cook With Gat\nv\nVirginia T P A\nSpecial to the Herald\nRoanoke Va May 22 This city is\ntoday the Mecca for commercial trav\nelers from all paits of Virginia the\noccasion being the seventeenth annual\nstate convention of the Traveleis\nProtective Association The conven\nf\ntion opened with President B B\nAdams of Lynchburg in the chair\nThe reports of SecretaryTreasurer H\nL Harwood of Richmond and of other\nofficers and committees contained fig\nures that showed a gratifying increase\nin the membership of the organiza\ntion and a satisfactory condition of\naffairs generally The convention will\nremain in session over tomorrow The\nentertainment program is an elabo\nrate one and with the business ses\nsions will keep the delegates exceed\ningly busy Numerous delegates\nmany of them accompanied by their\nwives arei in attendance from Rich\nmond Lynchburg Staunton Danville\nNewport News Petersburg Martins\nville and other Virginia cities\nFine Dewberries for sale\nRoedick No 577\nAT THE\nPhone H\n11lf\nMajestic\nENTIRE\nTONIGHT\nCHANGE OF\nPROGRAM\nHorwits Old Stand Main Street\nPROGRAM\nFlower Girl\nTit For Tat\nJealousy Tragedy of Old\nVenice Othello\nTHE MAJESTIC\nwill have an entire change of pro\ngram every night We have one of\nthe best makes of moving picture ma\nchines and will always try to get the\nvery best pictures that can be had\nAny feature subject that the public\nwould ike to see all they have to do\nis to let us know and we will do out\nbest to get it for them\nYours truly\nELLERD MAYFIELD\nFew Attractions\nFor the Lady Shopper Who Appreciates\nValue Style and Exclusive Patterns\nWASH SKIRTS\nJust a few samples by express in\nCopenhagen champagne and white\nbeautifully trimmed and so different\nfrom any seen this season\n375 to 500\nVOILE SKIRTS\nBrown black navy and champagne\nin small and extra sizes made of Alt\nmans Voile and trimmed in many dif\nferent designs uplo date and fit guar\nanteed The kind that sell for 15\n1G50 and 18 00 on sile this week\n1175\n4 WAISTS\nJap Sillc open front or back in black\nand white regular 450 kind in this\nweek sale 248\n10 dozen Lawn Waists regular 125\nand 150 kind ggc\nFrench Batiste and Lingerie Waists\nin seventeen different designs some\ntrimmed in Cluny Lace some German\nVal and Irish Point 298 348\n448 and 498\nWAISTS\nEcru and White Net trimmed with\ntwo rows of satin with lace collar and\nyoke regular 750 value on sale\n498\nBELTS\n10 dozen Wash Belts neat nnd dur\nable buckles in different patterns all\nsizes on sale 25c and 39c\nBlack Elastic made of best quality\nsilk elastic with gun metal and jet\nbuckles all sizes 75c to 98c\nMany different Novelties ranging\nfrom 50c to 198\nDRESSES\nSilk Jumper Net Lingerie and Wash\nDresses an array worthy of any city\nstore too many styles to give descrip\ntion so call and judge for yourself\nEvery garment guaranteed to fit\nMILLINERY\nOur closing out sale of this seasons\nPattern and Street Hats has left us\nwith only a few odds and ends which\ngo at a Sacrifice Also all flowers\nfeathers etc included\nTHE MODEL\nMitchell Furniture\nCompany\nFURNITURE MATTINGS RUGS\nSTOVES ETC\nWe Buy Old Furniture and Exchange New for\nOld Also Rent Chairs Tables Etc\nBuy NowPay Later\nTelephone 732\n518 Spring Street\nAustralian Tour For Miss Anglin\nSpecial to the Herald\nVictoria B Cr May 22 Miss Mar\ngaret Anglin the actress was among\nthe passengers sailing from here to\nday for Australia Miss Anglin plans\nto make a short starring tour in Aus\ntralia under the management of J C\nWilliamson When she returns next\nfall she will begin her season in New\nYork in The Awakening of Helen\nRitchie\nGet the Habit Cook With Gat\nAthletics and Oratory\nOklahoma City Okla May 22 The\nannual field and track meet and ora\ntorical contest of the Oklahoma Ora\nPalestine\nJ\ntorical and Intercollegiate Athletic\nAssociation attracted a large attend\nance here today and all signs at the\nopening pointed to a most successful\nmeeting The association embraces\nall the colleges of the state with the\nexception of the State University and\nEpworth University\nFuneral Notice\nDied near Quanah Texas Thurs\nday morning at six oclock Mrs Nan1\ncy Harriette Person born April IS\n1S25 Funeral service from the resi\ndence of Mr and Mrs T J Perkins\n506 Tennessee avenue 9 a m Satur\nday Friends and acquaintances are\ninvited Interment at Fort HoustonJ\ncemetery\nThe Globe Dry Goods Co\nOUR HOTTO Strictly Cash One Price to AH\no\nUR INAUGURAL SALE was such a grand success that\nit became necessary tor our Mr Herman Cohen to go\nto the Eastern markets in search of a complete new\nstock of goods and while there he will purchase the best goods\nthat can be gotten for the SPOT CASH Upon his return we\nwill display such a dazziing array of GENUINE BAR\nGAINS in all departments as will astonish the most skeptical\nbargain hunters\nWatch This Space For Our Announcement\nThe Globe Dry Goods Co\nOUR MOTTO Strictly Cash One Price to All","height":"27120","width":"18424"}}
